headline.main: Wijnaldum Says Consistency Key for Top-Four Ambitions
headline.print_headline: Wijnaldum Says Consistency Key for Top-Four Ambitions

lead_paragraph: Liverpool midfielder Georginio Wijnaldum is confident the side can deliver the results needed in their remaining 11 Premier League fixtures to ensure Champions League football next season.
